title: 01/29/2021 - HOUR 2 - Dallas Cowboys, John Middlekauf
itunes:title: 01/29/2021 - HOUR 2 - Dallas Cowboys, John Middlekauf
description:
In hour two, Doug advises the Dallas Cowboys should learn from others mistakes, and do not sign Dak to a long term contract and end up like the LA Rams. John Middlekauff also feels that the Houston Texans shouldn't trade Watson. And Green Bay doesn't want to be like Pittsburgh, stuck with an aging QB who may be on the down side.
